    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice the <strong>green chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</strong> </span>into rounds</p><p>Add the <strong>chilli rounds</strong> to a small bowl with the <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> and a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>sugar </strong>and set aside to pickle – these are your <strong>quick-pickled chillies</strong></p><p>Slice the <strong>black olives</strong> in half</p><p>Pick the<strong> basil leaves </strong>from their stems, discard the stems</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
