    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>pizza base mix</strong> to the bowl with the yeast</p><p>Gradually add up to 75ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml]</span> <strong>warm water </strong>(you may not need all of it) to the bowl, a little at a time, and gently mix with a plastic spatula until a sticky dough ball has formed</p><p>Tip the <strong>dough ball</strong> out onto a<strong> floured </strong>work surface and cut into 2<span class=\"text-danger\"> [4]</span></p><p>Toss each <strong>dough ball</strong> in a light dusting of <strong>flour </strong>until coated, rounding the ball as you go (no need to knead!)</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
