    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, carefully add the <strong>pizza base<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span></strong>to the pan<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span>, pushing the dough out to the edge to help shape the crust</p><p>Tip: To pick up the pizza dough, gently flip it over the back of your hand to stop it ripping!</p><p>Add 1/2<strong> </strong><span class=\"text-danger\">[1/4]</span> of the <strong>tomato sauce </strong>to each pizza and spread it evenly with the back of a spoon (be careful of the hot pan!)</p><p>Cook the pizza base<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> for 3-4 min or until the crust has started to puff up, then remove the heated tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span>from the oven and slide the pizza base<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]<strong> </span></strong>onto the tray</p>",
