    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash the <strong>rocket</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the<strong> rocket </strong>to a bowl with the <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>balsamic rocket</strong></p><p>Sprinkle the <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong> over the hot pizzas and serve the <strong>balsamic rocket</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
